				<td colspan="2"><span>I always use LoS to pull caster mobs. With the fix they put in last year, casting mobs now require LoS to cast on you. If you pop around a corner or get out of casting range, the mob will run up to you until it meets the requirements to cast. Positioned right, you can bring a caster mob to your group with just one or two casts.
<br />

<br />
Also, when pulling casting mobs I sing PoV immediately after the pull, inevitably I will get cast on but with PoV I stand a good chance of resisting everything, even lures.</span></td>
